%% Diagram: Figure 1 Statsig Sdk Evaluation Flow Server Sdks Perform Local Evaluation While
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
graph TB
    A[User Request] --> B{SDK Type?}
    B -->|Server SDK| C[Local Evaluation]
    B -->|Client SDK| D[Pre-evaluated Cache]

    C --> E[In-Memory Ruleset]
    E --> F[Deterministic Hash]
    F --> G[Result]

    D --> H[Local Storage Cache]
    H --> I[Network Request]
    I --> J[Statsig Backend]
    J --> K[Pre-computed Values]
    K --> L[Cache Update]
    L --> G

    G --> M[Feature Flag Result]

    style A fill:#e1f5fe
    style M fill:#c8e6c9
    style C fill:#fff3e0
    style D fill:#f3e5f5
